@startuml Complete System Sequence Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    BorderColor #2E86AB
    FontColor #1A365D
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2E86AB
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F7FAFC
    LifeLineBorderColor #4A5568
}

title Complete System Sequence Diagram
AI-Powered Project Management Platform (All 9 Modules)

actor "Project Manager" as PM
actor "Project Staff" as PS
actor "Financial Officer" as FO
actor "Auditor" as AU
actor "Field Staff" as FS
participant "Web Browser" as WB
participant "Mobile App" as MA
participant "Flask Application" as FA
participant "AI Engine" as AI
participant "Database" as DB

== Module 1: Project Monitoring & Performance ==

PM -> WB: Access project dashboard
WB -> FA: GET /dashboard
FA -> AI: get_performance_data()
AI -> DB: query_project_data()
DB --> AI: Project data
AI --> FA: Performance metrics
FA --> WB: Dashboard
WB --> PM: Display performance

== Module 2: Financial & Audit Management ==

FO -> WB: Access financial dashboard
WB -> FA: GET /financial/dashboard
FA -> AI: get_financial_data()
AI -> DB: query_financial_data()
DB --> AI: Financial data
AI -> AI: analyze_financial_patterns()
AI --> FA: Financial analysis
FA --> WB: Financial dashboard
WB --> FO: Display financial status

== Module 3: Risk Forecasting & Simulation ==

PM -> WB: View risk dashboard
WB -> FA: GET /risk/dashboard
FA -> AI: get_risk_data()
AI -> DB: query_risk_data()
DB --> AI: Risk data
AI -> AI: predict_risks()
AI --> FA: Risk predictions
FA --> WB: Risk dashboard
WB --> PM: Display risk assessment

== Module 4: Resource & Task Optimization ==

PM -> WB: Access resource dashboard
WB -> FA: GET /resources/dashboard
FA -> AI: get_resource_data()
AI -> DB: query_resource_data()
DB --> AI: Resource data
AI -> AI: optimize_resources()
AI --> FA: Resource optimization
FA --> WB: Resource dashboard
WB --> PM: Display resource optimization

== Module 5: Compliance & Guidance ==

AU -> WB: Access compliance dashboard
WB -> FA: GET /compliance/dashboard
FA -> AI: get_compliance_data()
AI -> DB: query_compliance_data()
DB --> AI: Compliance data
AI -> AI: check_compliance()
AI --> FA: Compliance status
FA --> WB: Compliance dashboard
WB --> AU: Display compliance status

== Module 6: Knowledge & Document Intelligence ==

PS -> WB: Upload document
WB -> FA: POST /upload_document
FA -> AI: process_document()
AI -> AI: extract_knowledge()
AI -> DB: store_knowledge()
DB --> AI: Knowledge stored
AI --> FA: Document processed
FA --> WB: Success
WB --> PS: Document uploaded

== Module 7: Communication Intelligence ==

PS -> WB: Send message
WB -> FA: POST /communication/send
FA -> AI: process_communication()
AI -> AI: analyze_communication()
AI -> DB: store_communication()
DB --> AI: Communication stored
AI --> FA: Communication processed
FA --> WB: Message sent
WB --> PS: Message sent

== Module 8: AI Guidance & Assistant ==

PM -> WB: Ask AI assistant
WB -> FA: POST /ai/chat
FA -> AI: process_query()
AI -> DB: query_knowledge()
DB --> AI: Knowledge data
AI -> AI: generate_response()
AI --> FA: AI response
FA --> WB: Response
WB --> PM: Display AI response

== Module 9: Mobile Monitoring & Alerts ==

FS -> MA: Access mobile app
MA -> FA: GET /mobile/dashboard
FA -> AI: get_mobile_data()
AI -> DB: query_mobile_data()
DB --> AI: Mobile data
AI --> FA: Mobile summary
FA --> MA: Mobile dashboard
MA --> FS: Display mobile interface

== Cross-Module Integration ==

note over AI: AI Engine coordinates all modules
AI -> DB: query_integrated_data()
DB --> AI: Integrated data
AI -> AI: process_cross_module_analysis()
AI -> FA: send_integrated_updates()
FA -> WB: Update all dashboards
FA -> MA: Update mobile interface
WB --> PM: Display integrated view
MA --> FS: Display integrated mobile view

@enduml





